    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Ecology",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Environment</b> warm deserts (Rahadoum)<br/><b>Organization</b> solitary, swarm (2\u20138), or plague (9\u201320)<br/><b>Treasure</b> none"
        },
        {
            "name": "Special Abilities",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Sawtooth (Ex)</b> The serrated mandibles of a stalk beetle allow it to ignore hardness of 5 or less when attacking objects. In addition, a stalk beetle deals 1 point of bleed damage upon a successful critical hit with its bite attack."
        },
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Stalk beetles are a plague in Rahadoum, scouring the land like giant locusts, and eating any and all vegetation they encounter."
        }
    ],
    "html": "<i>This ravenous beetle is the size of a pony, and sports a pair of deadly, serrated mandibles.</i>",
